fields.name: Tennis Club
fields.description: Tennis Club looks to provide recreational and competitive tennis activity for students. Our mission is to encourage and promote tennis as a way to keep healthy and fit.

fields.name: Fit-17
fields.description: Fitness exercies

fields.name: Football Club
fields.description: Football is in our blood. We train to improve skills and tactics, as well as to compete in various tournements. We are freindly and welcoming community. Join and have fun.

fields.name: RAGE
fields.description: This is a fellowship, united under the aegis of shared values and exercises in physical, spiritual and cultural dimensions. Learn more at club's page.

fields.name: LSD
fields.description: Our club is about supporting every sport beginner by getting them into a team to prepare for future competitions. Our main focus is crossfit and or slogan comes like that: commit to be fit. Our aims: Kazan marathon (Spring) and the Race of Heroes (Summer).

fields.name: Ping Pong Club
fields.description: Innopolis Ping Pong club is a sport club where you can find people with the same interests in table tennis and enjoy playing it. We run weekly meetings and some interesting competitions.

fields.name: Boxing Club
fields.description: The club is about practicing the art of boxing. The club aims at passing the art f boxing and technique to students of Innopolis University. We want to train 3 good instructors that would be able to deliver training sessions and also to recruit professional instructor.

fields.name: Skateboarding Club
fields.description: Our club is about honing skills in skateboarding and becoming more creative as skateboarding is one of the most creative kinds of sport. The most ultimate goal is to get to the first Olympic Games in Tokyo, but generally to evolve as skaters, and raise skaters' level up to the Russian-wide level.

fields.name: Cheerleading Club
fields.description: We learn cheearleading basics and combine it with acrobatic training. Open to all comers.

fields.name: Floorball Club
fields.description: The club is about training floorball skills and creating Innopolis University floorball team. We are aiming to organize at least one match vs a floorball team from Innopolis, Kazan or other city.

fields.name: Basketball club
fields.description: We create a team for regular trainings and participation in student and amateur leagues. Don't hesitate if you have never played, we'll make sure you become a good player!

fields.name: Volleyball Club
fields.description: Our club is growing as we train hard and improve technical aspects of the game. We are a friendly community of people who like hitting the ball over the net. We are waiting to see you at our sessions!

fields.name: Badminton Club
fields.description: The first Badminton club of Innopolis for students who have never held a racket before, as well as for those who are already familiar with it. We have some experienced players who are willing to introduce this sport to others. We are looking forward to compete in tournaments too.

fields.name: Street Workout
fields.description: Street workout consists of gimbarr, sport gymnastics, static and dynamic exercices on horizontal bar. Our goals are:  1) Making a team, introduction to basic exercices of street workout. 2) Create local workout competition.

fields.name: Sport fighting
fields.description: We are group of people who like Martial arts and several fighting sports. The goal is to train together, change experience and have fun within sports. We want to train students to be real gentlemen (gentlewomen) through sports.

fields.name: SAMBO/JUDO
fields.description: Sports activities always taught us restraint, discipline, rigor, as well as helped to keep ourselves in a good physical shape. What can be better than practicing real masculine sport under the guidance of experienced coaches? Be part of our team and learn this difficult but interesting art.

fields.name: Climbing Club
fields.description: We admire and get inspiration from natural rocks and beautiful caves. The main goal of our club is to develop climbing in Innopolis. Students are invited to travel and try rock climbing and other extreme sports.

fields.name: Chess Club
fields.description: We meet twice a week to play chess OTB, share knowledge, and discuss chess news and events from all over the world. We also hold different tournaments regularly. Everyone is welcome to join us - from beginners to professionals!

fields.name: Functional Pro Club
fields.description: Our Goal: to improve participation in sport among students. Keep healthy lifestyle. Develop strength, endurance. Create university team to participate in competitions.

fields.name: League of Sport Development
fields.description: Our club is about supporting every sport beginner by getting them into a team to prepare for future competitions. Our main focus is crossfit and or slogan comes like that: commit to be fit. Our aims: Kazan marathon (Spring) and the Race of Heroes (Summer).

fields.name: Sport fighting and self-defense Club's (POGO)
fields.description: We are group of people who like Martial arts and several fighting sports. The goal is to train together, change experience and have fun within sports. We want to train students to be real gentlemen (gentlewomen) through sports.
